description: The video shows a still shot from a security camera inside a shop. There is an open door leading to a street, with a metal grate over the doorway. Two coolers are visible to the left of the door. An individual off-camera is speaking Spanish.

The video shows a security camera view of a driveway. A black car is parked under a covered porch. There are trees and shrubs visible in the background. The camera is facing the driveway and a man is riding a bike down the driveway toward the camera. The man stops his bike and rings a bell.

The video shows a black and white night vision recording of a backyard. The camera is pointed downwards at a 45-degree angle. The backyard is mostly dark, but a few objects can be seen in the distance. A wooden fence, and what appears to be a shed or other structure, are visible in the distance.  There is a timestamp in the upper left corner of the screen: "2024-05-27 20:25:12."  The video is quiet and there is no sound.

The video is a recording from a security camera. The camera is pointed toward the street and a field. The field is visible in the background. The camera is mounted on the roof of a building. In the foreground, you can see the edge of a red roof, a brick wall, a green gate, and a patch of dirt with some loose bricks and a blue container. The date and time is displayed in the upper left corner. The camera is filming the field, the street and the roof of the building. It seems that there is no activity on the street, in the field or on the roof.

The video is a wide shot of a messy bedroom. A ceiling fan is spinning and a person can be heard talking, but the person is not visible in the frame. The bed has a white headboard, a pink and white blanket and a dark comforter and pillows. There are multiple items and clothes scattered on the bed.  There is a side table next to the bed with various items and a table lamp turned on. Another piece of furniture is visible in the foreground with drawers and various items piled on top.  The time stamp in the top left corner indicates that the video was recorded on May 28, 2024 at 2:52:25 PM. In the upper right corner, the word "yi" can be seen, which may be the brand of the camera. In the background, there is a shelf with various items, a whiteboard, a window with curtains, and a plush toy. A faint noise is heard throughout the video which sounds like the person may be making a phone call.  The video ends with a "p" sound and the word "need."

The video is a grainy black and white security camera recording of a street at night. Four vehicles are parked on the street, a white pickup truck, a dark pickup truck, a black SUV and a dark pickup truck that is only partially visible. There are two bright street lights in the background. The audio is a quiet humming sound.

The video shows a black and white still image of a bedroom. The image is dark and shows a bed, a dresser, and a door leading into another room. The audio is a female voice that repeatedly says "What? Why? You're part of the problem!" It sounds as if the speaker is frustrated or angry.  It's difficult to provide more context without a clearer image or more information about the audio.

The video is a still shot from a deck overlooking a backyard. The camera is looking through a gate toward a green grassy backyard. There are trees on either side of the yard and a line of power lines running across the top of the frame. In the center of the yard is a play set with a slide, a swing and a small wooden house-like structure. On the left side of the yard is a trampoline. The camera is slightly shaking.  A very faint bird chirping can be heard, and in the background what sounds like a lawnmower is faintly heard.

The video is a security camera footage showing a street in an urban area. The camera is pointed at a backyard. In the middle of the backyard is a small garage with an overhead door. The door is closed. There is also a wooden door to the left of the garage door. There is a basketball hoop on the garage. To the right of the garage is a black trash can. To the left of the garage door, is a blue trash can.  There is a  wooden fence separating the backyard from the street. There is a blue tarp covering a car parked on the street. A white SUV is parked in the street. To the left of the SUV are other cars parked in the street. There are houses on either side of the street. The camera is zoomed in, but there are trees and power lines visible in the background. The camera shows the cars in the street, the houses, and the backyard. It is a sunny day, with a few clouds in the sky.

The video shows a dark room. There are some lights on in the room and an outline of a person moving around. A small white object is shown moving in the top window pane. The video ends with a noise like a person clearing their throat.

The video shows a still image of a bakery. Two metal racks filled with freshly baked bread are visible in the foreground.  On the rack on the left are a few trays of what appears to be small, round buns, possibly filled with something sweet, such as chocolate or fruit. On the right rack are small crescent rolls. On the top of the rack on the right, there are two round metal cake pans and one larger rectangular pan. Above the racks, there are stacks of metal baking trays. A partially visible commercial oven is in the background. There is a very faint sound of a commercial oven as it operates.

The video shows a black SUV parked in a driveway. The camera is mounted on a house, and the angle is wide. There is a wooden porch to the right of the car, and a white van is parked behind the car. The sun is shining brightly, and the grass in the background is green.  There is a small blue object in the bottom left corner of the frame.  At the end of the video, you can hear a series of beeps.

The video shows a hallway in an apartment building. A man is walking down the hall, holding a walking stick, and walks past a camera which is mounted on the wall. He stops near a door and appears to be looking for something, possibly a keyhole, but it is difficult to tell without a clearer view of his hands. The video ends with him seemingly starting to walk again.

The video shows a hallway in a building. The camera is mounted high on the wall, facing down the hall. On the left side of the screen is a door, a fire extinguisher, and a small white shelf. The right side of the screen shows the continuation of the hallway. There is a sign that says "DISHROOM" above an intercom. The hallway is empty, and the walls are a light beige.  The time stamp at the top of the screen is 2024-05-28 11:42:50.

The video is a night-time surveillance recording from a security camera. The camera is mounted high on the front of a house, facing towards a sidewalk. The sidewalk is made of concrete slabs and runs from the front gate to the street. The sidewalk is flanked by patches of grass and a chain-link fence. The video shows two garbage cans in the foreground, one black and one blue. The black can is slightly larger than the blue one and has a white plastic bag over the top.  The blue can is partially visible on the right side of the frame and has recycling logos on it. There are no other objects or people in view, and the camera footage is fairly static, although a few things can be heard. The camera appears to be slightly zoomed in on the garbage cans, and it picks up sounds of rustling leaves and a dog barking in the background. The video is not long and cuts out before the dog's bark finishes.

The video starts with a man sitting in a chair in a living room.  He is watching television.  The TV is showing a woman in an apron cooking.  The man is pointing at the TV screen with his left hand. He is wearing a blue shirt and black shorts.  The television is positioned above a fireplace that has a decorative bird sculpture on it.  The man then turns to the right to grab something from the kitchen counter that is partially visible behind him.  The kitchen counter has several glass cabinets, and a coffee machine is visible on the counter.  The man's right hand is holding a remote control.  He then returns to his seat and continues watching television.

The video is a home security camera recording of a suburban street. There are two cars in the driveway, a silver BMW on the right and a white car on the left. The BMW is parked in the driveway and the white car is partly parked on the driveway and partly on the street. The front of the driveway is empty with a paved street leading into the distance.  The street is lined with green grass and a fence. Behind the fence is a house with pink siding. The video ends with a dog barking in the distance.

The video is a security camera recording from a high angle view. The footage is grainy and has a limited field of view, capturing a small portion of a concrete yard with a patch of green grass. In the distance, a road is visible, and there are a few pieces of debris in the yard.  At around the 3 second mark, the upper portion of a white van can be seen driving past the camera. The van is very briefly visible in the frame. The video continues with no other activity aside from the wind blowing, and then it cuts off abruptly.

The video shows a security camera recording in a dimly lit room. The camera has night vision, resulting in a black-and-white image. The room has a concrete floor and white walls. There is a metal shelving unit in the bottom left corner of the room. A white filing cabinet is in front of the shelves. The room also contains a door and a toolbox on a rolling cart.  The camera pans slowly around the room. No one is visible in the video. At the end, a sound that could be a high-pitched beeping noise, or a dripping sound, is audible.

The video is taken from a security camera. The camera is facing a house with a driveway and a road in front of it. There are several trees in the yard and a sign that reads "5 mph". There are two cars parked in the driveway. There is a truck driving on the road. There are also some animals in the yard. They look like black dogs. The video is grainy and the camera appears to have a wide-angle lens. The video starts with a truck driving on the road and then focuses on the cars parked in the driveway. The truck drives past the camera and disappears in the distance. Then there is a white SUV driving on the road and the video stops.

The video starts with a shot of a window screen with green trees and grass visible in the background.  The sound of a man's voice asking what someone is doing in a hostile manner can be heard.  The voice describes the man's brother's death and says that he is related to John's crank, which could be an individual or a thing.  The video ends with the man concluding that there is a game going on.

The video shows a night-time view from a security camera positioned on a front porch. There are two columns on either side of the camera view.  We see a short brick pathway leading out to a street. The grass is dark in the video, but there is a streetlight illuminating the street and giving off a faint glow on the grass. There is a small object that appears to be a potted plant just inside the edge of the camera view. The camera’s motion sensor activates around the 0:29 mark when we see a small black and white animal, which appears to be a cat, walk into the camera view and leave again. It doesn’t appear to notice the camera.

The video shows a security camera view of a front porch. The door is open and a wicker chair is to the left of the doorway. A concrete walkway extends to the right, leading to a green lawn. A small stone step is in front of the chair. The camera appears to be mounted inside the house, looking out at the porch.  At 00:30, a beep sound can be heard.

The video shows a security camera view of a street corner. A blue trash can and a black trash can are visible on the right side of the screen, next to a sidewalk. To the left of the sidewalk is a white car partially visible. A dark-colored SUV is parked partially on the right side of the screen. On the opposite side of the street is a small grassy island with a circular driveway around it. Two cars are seen driving counterclockwise around the roundabout in the distance. The video ends as a loud "Beep Beep Beep" sound is heard.

The video is a black and white night time recording of a flat, paved area.  The camera is pointed at the ground.  The sound is of a single, high-pitched, repeating "beep" sound that is slightly distorted.   There is no movement in the video.

The video shows a room with a white wall, a gray couch with an orange pillow, and a water cooler in the left side of the screen. The water cooler is on a wooden stand. The water in the container is blue. The room is empty and has tiled floors.  A date and time stamp is shown in the top left corner. An audio track plays Spanish, but the words are unclear.

The video shows a black and white security camera footage of two objects hanging from the ceiling in a room. The objects are swinging back and forth. There are two leather armchairs in the background, a side table with a plastic bag and some bottles on it, and a small table with a tray and some items on it in the foreground. There are some other objects on the floor around the table, including a small plastic cup. The timestamp in the top left corner indicates that the footage was taken on 2024-05-28 at 08:40:23. A loud peeping sound can be heard in the background.

The video shows a man in a black shirt and green pants standing in a room with a gray wall. He is facing a doorway with a kitchen in the background. There are two light switches on the wall to his right, and a chandelier hanging from the ceiling. There is a gold cart with a coffee maker and other items on it in the lower left corner of the frame. A pink towel is draped over a chair in the background. He reaches into a bag on the floor and pulls out a black speaker. He looks at it, then puts it back into the bag. The video ends with him reaching into the bag once more.

The video shows a black and white still image of a storage area. The camera is positioned in the corner of the room facing a metal shelf with white plastic storage bins. The bins are filled with what appears to be white fabric. The labels on the bins are not visible. Some boxes are stacked on the upper left side of the image. The entire room is dimly lit with only a few spots of light illuminating the subject.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera. It shows a ceiling fan spinning with an air vent in the bottom left corner of the frame.  The date and time stamp appears in the top left of the frame. There is an unidentified voice in the background, speaking in a foreign language.  The camera is pointed directly upward at the fan.  The video is short and only captures about 30 seconds of footage.

The video shows a suburban street on a sunny day. The camera is mounted on the front porch of a house. In the foreground, there is a lawn with a set of bird feeders, including two large brown and white containers and a small bowl. A large tree is growing near the right side of the lawn, and several plants are growing in a flower bed near the bottom right of the screen. A brick post on the left side of the screen is the camera's mount. In the background, a white SUV is pulling into the driveway of the house. The camera pans slightly to the right, showing the front of the house. The house has a brick facade with a white porch. A large tree with green leaves is visible in the background on the left. The SUV has pulled into the driveway and stopped. A person gets out of the driver's side door and walks toward the mailbox. The video ends before the person can reach the mailbox.

The video shows a close-up of a small, gray cage with a wire mesh top. The cage is sitting on a carpeted floor. Inside the cage is a brown substrate and a green leafy plant, along with a small, gray ramp. The cage has an electronic device on the outside, connected to the wire mesh top. The camera angle is slightly above the cage, and the video is very still. The sound is quiet, and only a faint beeping noise can be heard at the end.

The video starts with a black and white shot of a hallway in a house.  The camera is mounted on the wall and pointing down the hallway.  The hallway is empty except for two white doors on either side of the camera. The camera then switches to color and we see a person walking down the hallway towards the camera. They are wearing a tank top and grey pants.  They are carrying a flashlight and are shining it on the wall as they walk. The person walks into a room at the end of the hallway.  The camera then zooms in on the door the person entered, and there is a lot of movement in the room for a few seconds. The camera then pans back to the hallway and the person is no longer there.  We hear a strange noise, like a whimpering or screeching, and the video cuts to black.  It is unclear what exactly the person was doing in the room.  The whimpering sound may be from a pet or some other unknown source. The video is a bit unsettling and raises more questions than it answers.

The video is a grainy, blurry, low-resolution security camera shot. The camera is pointed toward the ground with the lens tilted slightly upward. A few black specks can be seen moving across the frame, perhaps insects or dust. The only sound is a constant, low, buzzing sound. It is difficult to tell what the purpose of the camera is or where it is located.

The video is a static shot from a security camera mounted on the side of a mobile home. The camera is pointed toward a small yard with a wooden deck, two tables, a lawnmower, and a red SUV parked in the driveway. The trees and houses in the background suggest a suburban setting. The video is silent and there is no movement. The video appears to have been recorded in the summer.

The video is a close-up shot of a window. The camera is mounted outside, so the window is being viewed from the exterior. You can see the white siding of the house and some green grass. Through the window, you can see a reflection of the backyard, which contains a path, some green grass and a red bird feeder hanging from a tree. The video is very still and only captures the movement of the bird feeder being gently swayed by the wind. It is a very quiet video and the only sound you can hear is the occasional "Peep" noise, which is likely made by the birds at the feeder.

This is a security camera video of a house’s front porch. The camera is mounted on the porch, facing out toward the sidewalk and the front door. The door is closed, and a red welcome mat is visible. The porch has a white railing, and there is a brick pillar to the right of the door. The ground is a light gray concrete. The video begins in the middle of the day, as the sun is shining. There is a small brown sign to the right of the walkway, which is partly in the shadows. The sidewalk is gray concrete, and there is a green lawn to the right of the sidewalk. A sound of a dog barking is heard starting at 0:25.

The video is in black and white and appears to be from a security camera. The video shows a small dog, possibly a white Maltese or a bichon frise, standing on a bed and looking down at a person sleeping under the covers. The dog seems to be contemplating jumping on the bed and wakes up the sleeping person, who moves to let the dog on. The dog then jumps on the bed and curls up beside the sleeping person, who continues to sleep. The video ends with the dog and the sleeping person together on the bed.

The video is a security camera recording from an industrial warehouse or storage facility.  The camera is mounted on the wall and angled slightly down.  There is a red fire sprinkler pipe in the left side of the frame.  In the center, a table has a water cooler with two 5-gallon jugs, a black desktop computer monitor, and a multi-function printer. The floor is concrete with yellow caution tape markings.  There is shelving in the background with some boxes on the shelves.  There are several boxes on the floor in the left side of the frame.  In the foreground right side of the frame, there is a stack of cardboard boxes on a pallet.  On the right side of the frame is a man in a gray t-shirt and a white baseball cap.  He is holding a large cardboard box in his right hand and is lifting it from a pallet.  Behind him is another man in a green t-shirt who is walking to the left, holding some papers in his left hand.  The man in the green t-shirt stops in the center of the frame and bends over to look at the papers.  He then walks back to the right and continues to follow the man in the gray t-shirt, who has now lifted the box and is carrying it toward the back of the room.  As they are walking, an electrical fan and a black floor fan are visible in the background.  The man in the green t-shirt walks past the camera and is no longer visible.  The man in the gray t-shirt walks to the left and out of the frame.  The camera remains focused on the space where the men were standing.  The video has audio of the background noise from the warehouse.

The video shows a security camera view of a room with wooden floors. There are five chairs, stacked upside down. The camera is angled so that the chairs look distorted and like they're tilted forward, despite being upright. The date and time stamp is shown in the top left corner: "2024-05-28 06:45:34". The chairs are made of light grey wood with dark grey padding on the seats. The video is very still and the only movement is a slight flicker of light on the floor from a light source outside of the camera's view. At 0:25 there is a noise that sounds like "peep peep peep".

The video is a black and white security camera footage. It appears to be taken inside a house or apartment.  There is a closed white door on the left side of the screen. There is a table in the middle of the screen, with items on it. There is a tall, rectangular object on the left that looks like a flat screen TV. There are some unidentified rectangular boxes on the table. In the distance, on the right side of the screen, there are two closed doors. There is a shelf on the wall with various items on it.

The video is a grainy black and white security camera recording of a room. The room appears to be an indoor gym with exercise equipment visible in the background. A person is standing near a tall object in the center of the room, moving their arms. The camera is angled slightly up from the ground. There are a few bright lights flickering outside the windows of the room, possibly streetlights. A beep sound is audible in the video.

The video is a still shot taken from a security camera.  It shows a dark grey pickup truck parked in a driveway in front of a wooden fence. There are two white trailers parked in the distance. It is a cloudy day and it appears to be raining. The timestamp on the video says 05/28/2024 at 17:12.

The video shows three candles: one green, one red and one in a glass.  The red candle is lit and the green candle is lit for a moment.  The video shows the red candle burning for about 20 seconds with no other movement or change. The time stamp at the top left of the screen shows 2024-05-28 18:07:50 through 2024-05-28 18:08:14. The glass candle appears to be partially filled with white wax. It has a date written on the outside of it, “28/May 10:25 AM.”  The video likely shows a test of a candle or is part of a larger experiment.

The video shows a black snake slithering across a dirt path. The snake is moving from left to right and is clearly visible. The snake is in the foreground of the shot, and there is a paved road in the background. There are trees and bushes on either side of the path, and a white building with a red roof can be seen in the distance. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the screen. There is some audio of nature sounds, like birds chirping.

The video shows a small dog running around in a living room with a large folding chair in the background. The dog is running around the room, seemingly looking for something, and is then startled by something off screen. The dog then quickly runs out of frame.

The video shows a static shot of a covered porch overlooking a canal. It is a sunny day. The camera is pointed upwards and is looking out of the windows. There is a small boat docked at the pier in the distance. The sound of seagulls and waves can be heard. The video ends with a beep sound effect.

The video shows a man sanding a white door that is laying horizontally on sawhorses in a wet workshop. The man is wearing a blue shirt and black pants and a black hat. The workshop is partially open and the weather is rainy. You can see a yellow car and other vehicles in the background, as well as a brick wall and a portion of a chainlink fence. The man is sanding the door with an electric sander. There is a power cord attached to the sander and running across the floor.  The audio in the video is a man speaking in an unknown language, but the speech is unintelligible.

The video is a black and white night time surveillance recording of a white van parked in a driveway. The van is parked on the right side of the screen, and there is a white vertical post in the middle of the screen. There is a black grill to the left of the post and two barrels to the right of the van. A few branches from a tree are visible above the van. The only sound is of what appears to be a lawnmower running in the distance. There is no movement of the van or any other objects in the video.

The video shows a backyard during a light downpour. A tall wooden fence separates the backyard from a narrow alleyway made of brick and dirt. The camera is situated on the left side of the frame, overlooking the alleyway and the fence. The right side of the frame shows the backyard, which features a patch of green grass, a small air conditioning unit, and a brick building with a window and a door.  There are also some red plastic toys and a white object in the backyard. The sound of light rain is heard throughout the video, followed by a loud "p" sound that appears to be a dog barking.

The video shows a man in a red shirt pulling a black grill on wheels out of the back of a black pickup truck. The truck is parked on a dirt driveway with green grass on either side. There are trees and a chain-link fence in the background. The man struggles to pull the grill as it seems to be stuck on the truck bed. The truck then backs up and the man pushes the grill further out of the truck bed and into the grass. The truck continues backing up. The man is no longer visible in the frame and the truck continues to back up until it is completely out of view.  The timestamp on the video is 05/28/2024 15:48:41.

The video shows a security camera view of a bedroom. It is a wide shot showing a bed with a white mattress and a wooden frame. The bed is made, but there is an orange blanket folded at the foot of the bed and a gray blanket partially covering a white armchair on the right side of the screen. The camera appears to be attached to the wall in the top left corner of the room. There is a white door in the back left corner of the room that is partly open. It is hard to see details of the room through the door, but a wicker basket is visible on the floor. There is a side table to the right of the armchair with a white lamp on it. There is a white wall with decorative dinosaur garland hanging on it. The digital clock on the side table reads 1:30. The date and time are shown in the top left corner of the video as 05/28/2024 12:49:57. A man in a gray shirt and shorts enters the room at 00:11, steps over the blanket at the foot of the bed, and exits through the door at 00:13. The camera continues to record the empty room for another 27 seconds.

The video shows an elderly woman in a bedroom, sitting on the edge of a bed. She is wearing a beige sleeveless nightgown with a floral pattern.  Her grey hair is pulled back. She is looking at the television, which is showing a scene of a beach with a blue sky and waves. She is holding a remote control in her right hand. She is slowly flipping through channels. The room is cluttered with items on the nightstand, including an alarm clock, a phone, and a glass of water. There is a walker next to the television. Brown curtains are drawn behind her. The date and time are visible in the upper left corner, indicating it is May 27th, 2024, at 9:39 PM.

The video shows a security camera view of a parking lot. The camera is pointed at the ground looking up, with a red truck in the foreground. There are 5 other cars parked in the lot. The truck is in park, and its engine is running, as evidenced by the loud hum of the engine. The truck's driver's door is open, but the driver is not in the truck. After about 30 seconds, the engine shuts off, and the sound of a car door closing can be heard.

The video is a close-up of a piece of wood, possibly part of a fence post or railing. The wood is a light gray color and has a rough, textured surface. The video is blurry and does not show any interesting details or movement. The timestamp in the top left corner indicates that the video was recorded on May 28, 2024, at 10:32:47. There is a high-pitched, repetitive whistling sound that begins at the start of the video, which may be the sound of the wind blowing past the camera.

The video is a black and white security camera footage of a woman in a kitchen. At the beginning of the video, the woman enters the room from the left carrying a white blanket. She walks towards the couch where a person, out of view, is laying on the couch with a pillow. The woman walks across the room and exits through a door on the right side of the frame. A dog follows her out the door. She then re-enters the room from the door on the right and places the blanket on the couch before exiting through the same door on the right. The camera angle shifts to a view of the kitchen. The woman re-enters the room from the right and is seen standing to the left of the kitchen sink. She is wearing a light colored shirt and black leggings. The woman is seen wiping her hands on a towel.There is a lot of clutter in the kitchen. A large red bowl, a yellow bowl, a bottle of hand soap, a blue plastic bin, a roll of paper towels, a microwave, a toaster oven and a white refrigerator are visible. The woman is seen talking on her cell phone as she looks at a coffee maker. She then walks over to the sink and washes her hands. The video ends with the woman standing at the sink.

The video is a still shot of a backyard. It's a sunny day, and there is a lot of greenery. The camera is mounted on a wooden deck with a red railing. In the distance, you can see two houses, a swing set, a slide, and a trampoline. The wind rustles the leaves of the trees in the background.

The video shows a security camera's view of the inside of a house. The camera is positioned at the bottom of a flight of stairs, looking up. The camera has a fish-eye lens, so the view is distorted. On the left side of the video, there is a doorway that appears to be closed with a glass window that is partially obscured by a plant. The camera is pointed at a wooden staircase with an open doorway at the top. The wall is light-colored, and there are two light switches visible. An open doorway can be seen on the right side of the video, with a white door. A cardboard box can be seen on the top step of the staircase, to the left of the doorway. The video is very dark and the only light is coming from the doorway at the top of the stairs. In the audio, there is a repetitive ringing sound, like an alarm.  It sounds like a smoke alarm going off.  The alarm is going off in the hallway.

The video is a wide shot of a child's bedroom with a messy floor. The room is brightly lit and has a light blue wall. There are several toys scattered on the floor, including cars, stuffed animals, a dollhouse, a red tricycle, a broom, and a shovel. The bed is in the background and is covered with toys, blankets, and pillows. A gray dresser with five drawers is in the corner of the room. The door to the bedroom is closed, and a black dog is laying on the bed. A string of light bulbs hangs over the bed and is turned on. The camera is angled slightly upwards. A child's voice can be heard speaking but it is difficult to understand what is being said.  The timestamp at the top of the screen shows May 28th, 2024 at 9:44:22 AM.

The video shows a close-up of a security camera aimed at an exterior door. The camera is mounted under the eave of the roof. A white door with a white wrought iron gate in front of it is in the middle of the frame, and the bottom half of the door is visible to the left. A person with a long mop handle is visible to the right of the door. The mop is at the top of the frame. The person is using the mop to try to reach something just outside the frame, but it is not clear what they are trying to reach. The person is trying to get into the house, but it appears the door is locked. The person is using the mop to try to open the door, but the video is too short to tell if they are successful. The time on the camera is 2024-05-28 13:52:42 when the video starts.

The video starts with a woman in a black shirt and towel on her head walking into the kitchen from the doorway in the back of the frame. She is carrying a bottle of what appears to be hand sanitizer. Two small dogs run to greet her. The woman puts down the hand sanitizer on the kitchen island in front of a plate of fruit. A man is walking toward her from the left side of the frame. He is carrying a brown paper bag with a red tag and a backpack.
